    • Method Detail

      • getSurrogateKeyValue

        Object getSurrogateKeyValue(String[] naturalKeyValues,
                          Map<String,String> globalAttributes,
                          DimensionCache dimensionCache)
        Method invoked by StreamHorizon engine when it can not find mapping natural key -> surrogate key.
        Parameters:
        naturalKeyValues - the values for natural key for which surrogate key was not found. Ordered as defined in configuration file.
        globalAttributes - all context attributes available
        dimensionCache - the cache for this dimension
        Returns:
        surrogate key. Can be null.
